Subject: Tried to change server IP address but no UI access afterwards
Description: Tried to change the server to a new address.  After the change, ping and SSH could reach the new IP.  Accessing UI was not working.  Client port is 443 but admin port was changed to 8443.  Not sure if NGINX proxy config needs to be changed as well.
Solution_Comment__c: We adjusted the port of the Server IP in the configuration file + the Client IP. After that it worked
